{"tid":1726982,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咪傻 諗住吹抗爭玩完既風啦，出老解只係代表抗爭進入新階段","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:14:36.000Z","uid":161430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7aff16a98704485147dfa694e6ae208d9cb6c87","tid":1726982,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"代表香港人由以前既71遊行，行禮如儀，激嬲共產黨，<br />\n<br />\n到2014 捉鬼、自己分化自己既抗爭，<br />\n<br />\n進化到後來有梁天琦，魚革一夜，<br />\n<br />\n再進化到2019既抗爭，集合曬過去失敗經驗，慢慢改良，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>終於令對方知道，單靠班警察都冇撚柒用，<br />\n幫唔成手仲愈搞愈衰，所以先開始要諗出老解。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁呢件事係代表香港人向前行緊，<br />\n冇退化，亦都唔係玩完。<br />\n<br />\n星期開始，一樣會有新一輪抗爭，新既日程表。<br />\n想吹失敗既風？冇撚用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff1c5ba5654cc63d0f12efe0642e922d648381d","tid":1726982,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"9a6a34aa972f6475190b1c8a0681846985e1fda9","tid":1726982,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到攬抄為止"},{"pid":"46f3542bab7359f8c7f88cf4adb7a160ee78b885","tid":1726982,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"一齊retweet<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/rthk_enews/status/1195620490066284545?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frthk_enews%2Fstatus%2F119562